'''瑞安的世界'''（{{lang-en|Ryan's World}}），前称'''瑞安玩具测评'''（{{lang-en|Ryan ToysReview}}），是[[YouTube|YouTube]]上的儿童类频道，其[[YouTuber|YouTuber]]为来自[[美国|美国]][[得克萨斯州|得克萨斯州]]的儿童瑞安·卡吉（Ryan Kaji）<ref name = "Ad Age">{{cite magazine|title=New Kids on the Block: Move over Gen Z, Generation Alpha is the one to watch|url=https://adage.com/article/cmo-strategy/move-gen-z-generation-alpha-watch/316314|last1=Pasquarelli|first1=Adrianne|last2=Schultz|first2=E.J.|work=[[广告时代|Ad Age]]|volume=90|issue=2|page=22|date= 2019-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190123042540/https://adage.com/article/cmo-strategy/move-gen-z-generation-alpha-watch/316314/|archive-date=2019-01-23}}</ref> 。瑞安的家庭同时运营9个YouTube频道，而该频道是其全部运营频道中最受欢迎的<ref name=ckxx>{{cite news |title=年收入近3000万美元 英媒：9岁男孩蝉联最赚钱视频主播 |url=http://www.cankaoxiaoxi.com/culture/20201221/2427638.shtml |accessdate=2020-12-27 |work=参考消息网 |date=2020-12-21 |archive-date=2021-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220050339/http://www.cankaoxiaoxi.com/culture/20201221/2427638.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

该频道幾乎每日都有新片上載，内容为新款玩具開箱及試玩、DIY科学实验及家庭故事等<ref name="oncc">{{cite news |title=8歲童成最吸金YouTuber 介紹玩具年賺2200萬美元 |url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20181204/bkn-20181204110601917-1204_00972_001.html |accessdate=2020-12-27 |work=on.cc東網 |date=2018-12-04 |language=zh-hk}}</ref>，其中一条视频《巨型惊喜玩具蛋挑战》（''Huge Eggs Surprise Toys Challenge''）观看次数达20亿次以上，成为YouTube上[[觀看次數最多的YouTube影片列表|观看次数最多的60个视频]]之一<ref name=ckxx/>。2020年，瑞安·卡吉通过该频道获得了2950万美元的收入，另外还从同名品牌玩具和服装销售中获得2亿美元。在《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志公布的全球YouTuber收入排行榜中，瑞安·卡吉自2018年以来连续三年位居榜首<ref>{{cite news |title=福布斯公布YouTube网红收入榜 9岁男孩Ryan Kaji第三次登榜首 |url=https://fashion.sina.com.cn/l/fa/2020-12-23/0959/doc-iiznctke8005382.shtml |accessdate=2020-12-27 |work=新浪时尚 |date=2020-12-23 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126085944/https://fashion.sina.com.cn/l/fa/2020-12-23/0959/doc-iiznctke8005382.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=年收入 1.93 亿元，9 岁男孩玩玩具蝉联最赚钱 YouTube 视频主播 |url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-12-21/doc-iiznctke7681680.shtml |accessdate=2020-12-27 |work=IT之家 |date=2020-12-21}}</ref>。

==背景及历史==
2015年3月，瑞安·卡吉在YouTube上观看完其他玩具测评频道后，他很快跟妈妈说：“别的孩子都可以拍自己玩玩具的视频，我行不行呢？”于是瑞安很快就有了建立自己的YouTube频道的想法<ref name="WP2017">{{cite news|last=Schmidt|first=Samantha|title=6-year-old made $11 million in one year reviewing toys on You Tube|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2017/12/11/6-year-old-made-11-million-in-one-year-reviewing-toys-on-you-tube/|work=[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]|access-date=2020-12-27|date=2017-12-11|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110141137/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2017/12/11/6-year-old-made-11-million-in-one-year-reviewing-toys-on-you-tube/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。瑞安的母亲也决定辞去高中化学老师的工作，全职运营其儿子开设的YouTube频道<ref name="Verge2016">{{cite web|last=Popper|first=Ben|title=YouTube's biggest star is a 5-year-old that makes millions opening toys|url=https://www.theverge.com/2016/12/22/14031288/ryan-toys-review-biggest-youngest-youtube-star-millions|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|date=2016-12-22|access-date=2020-12-27|archive-date=2021-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322172044/https://www.theverge.com/2016/12/22/14031288/ryan-toys-review-biggest-youngest-youtube-star-millions|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年，瑞安的父母与儿童传媒公司{{le|PocketWatch|PocketWatch (company)}}签约，PocketWatch公司全权负责YouTube频道的营销和同名商品销售的工作<ref name="pocket.watch">{{cite web|title=7-year-old toy reviewer on YouTube becomes a toy himself|url=https://whdh.com/news/7-year-old-toy-reviewer-on-youtube-becomes-a-toy-himself/|publisher=WHDH|agency=[[美联社|美联社]]|date=2018-10-03|access-date=2018-10-03|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206173445/https://whdh.com/news/7-year-old-toy-reviewer-on-youtube-becomes-a-toy-himself/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年，该频道与PocketWatch、{{le|WildWorks|WildWorks}}联合推出儿童[[跑酷|跑酷]]手機游戏 "Tag with Ryan"<ref name="tagwithryan">{{cite web|url=https://tagwithryan.com/|title=Tag with Ryan|publisher=WildWorks|access-date=2020-12-27|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308203718/https://tagwithryan.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年，Outright Games又推出了瑞安同名电子游戏《瑞安小赛车》（''Race with Ryan''）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.outrightgames.com/racewithryan|title=Race With Ryan Road Trip Deluxe Edition|website=Outright Games|access-date=2019-12-01|archive-date=2020-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200115151156/https://www.outrightgames.com/racewithryan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，瑞安也与PocketWatch合作，制作20集系列电视节目《瑞安神秘玩耍记》（''Ryan's Mystery Playdate''），在[[尼克国际儿童频道|尼克国际儿童频道]]播出<ref name="tvshow">{{cite web|last=Zahn|first=James|url=https://toybook.com/from-youtube-to-nickelodeon-ryans-mystery-playdate-is-the-next-move-for-ryan-toysreview/|title=From YouTube to Nickelodeon: Ryan's Mystery Playdate is the Next Move for Ryan ToysReview|date=2019-02-14|website=The Toy Book|access-date=2020-11-20|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806125434/https://toybook.com/from-youtube-to-nickelodeon-ryans-mystery-playdate-is-the-next-move-for-ryan-toysreview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该频道宣布于2020年11月27日在Amazon Kids+上首播集真人与动画为一体的电视剧《超级间谍瑞安》（''Super Spy Ryan''）<ref>{{Cite web |last=Alexander |first=Julia |date=2020-11-19 |title=YouTube's biggest child star is getting his own show on Amazon |url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/11/19/21575169/youtube-ryan-world-amazon-show-animated-nickelodeon-ott-streaming |access-date=2020-11-22 |website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126051839/https://www.theverge.com/2020/11/19/21575169/youtube-ryan-world-amazon-show-animated-nickelodeon-ott-streaming |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年12月4日，该频道宣布在[[機器磚塊|機器磚塊]]游戏平台推出以瑞安为名的游戏<ref name="Patel">{{cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/9-year-old-youtube-star-ryan-kaji-opens-virtual-world-on-roblox-11607079600|title=9-Year-Old YouTube Star Ryan Kaji Opens Virtual World on Roblox|work=华尔街日报|last=Patel|first=Sahil|date=2020-12-04|access-date=2020-12-08|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302145412/https://www.wsj.com/articles/9-year-old-youtube-star-ryan-kaji-opens-virtual-world-on-roblox-11607079600|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==影响==
瑞安·卡吉开设的频道影响了整个玩具行业。他的玩具测评，尤其是获得上百万次观看的测评，有时会影响玩具的销量{{r|"Verge2016"}}，由他推介過的玩具都會在短时间内售罄<ref name="oncc"/>。PocketWatch公司曾将瑞安·卡吉与《[[海绵宝宝|海绵宝宝]]》相提并论{{r|"pocket.watch"}}。

在2018年[[美國國際玩具展覽會|美國國際玩具展覽會]]上，瑞安与PocketWatch、Bonkers Toys合作推出了“瑞安的世界”系列玩具產品<ref>{{Cite press release|url=http://pocket.watch/press/press-release-february-13-2018|title=Major Apparel and Toy Companies Jump On Board pocket.watch Media Brand|date=2018-02-13|website=pocket.watch|access-date=2018-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724154007/http://pocket.watch/press/press-release-february-13-2018|archive-date=2018-07-24}}</ref>。同年8月6日，此系列玩具在[[沃尔玛|沃尔玛]]各门店独家发售<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.i4u.com/2018/07/129218/ryan-toysreview-launches-massive-ryans-world-toy-line-exclusively-walmart|title=Ryan ToysReview Launches Massive Ryan's World Toy Line-up Exclusively at Walmart|last=Lugmayr|first=Luigi |website=I4U News|date=2018-07-30|access-date=2018-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180730150144/https://www.i4u.com/2018/07/129218/ryan-toysreview-launches-massive-ryans-world-toy-line-exclusively-walmart|archive-date=2018-07-30}}</ref>。

2018年12月，《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志公布全球YouTuber收入排行榜，瑞安以2200萬美元的收入位居榜首<ref name="oncc"/>。之后在2019年<ref name="Forbes2019">{{cite magazine|first=Madeline|last=Berg|title=The Highest-Paid YouTube Stars of 2019: The Kids Are Killing It|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/maddieberg/2019/12/18/the-highest-paid-youtube-stars-of-2019-the-kids-are-killing-it/|magazine=Forbes|date=2019-12-18|access-date=2019-12-23|archive-date=2020-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130164301/https://www.forbes.com/sites/maddieberg/2019/12/18/the-highest-paid-youtube-stars-of-2019-the-kids-are-killing-it/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、2020年<ref name=ckxx/>蝉联榜首位置。瑞安的收入大部分來自播放影片前的廣告，以及海量的訂閱者。由於他仍是未成年人，他的15%薪酬須存入銀行，成年後才可提取<ref name="oncc"/>。

==争议==
2019年8月，美国[[联邦贸易委员会|联邦贸易委员会]]及消费监督组织“{{le|Truth in Advertising|Truth in Advertising}}”指控“瑞安的世界”频道没有認真地公布视频的赞助商。指控中提到“在此视频中，近90%的视频至少包括一个针对学龄前儿童的付费产品推荐，这个群体太小，无法区分广告和评论。”而TIA表示“这些广告經常宣傳垃圾食品”<ref name=ckxx/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/04/business/media/ryan-toysreview-youtube-ad-income.html|title=Popular YouTube Toy Review Channel Accused of Blurring Lines for Ads|last=Hsu|first=Tiffany|date=2019-09-04|work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|access-date=2020-12-27|archive-date=2022-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220102075346/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/04/business/media/ryan-toysreview-youtube-ad-income.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/26/well/family/Youtube-children-junk-food-child-obesity.html|title=Are 'Kidfluencers' Making Our Kids Fat?|last=O'Connor|first=Anahad|date=2020-10-26|work=纽约时报|access-date=2020-12-27|archive-date=2022-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220102075359/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/26/well/family/Youtube-children-junk-food-child-obesity.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

